OL,6,FA letter signed "Madeleine X" was
OL,7,Fposted through the door of Madeleine
OL,8,FMcCann's parents' home the day after
OL,9,Ftwo women accused of stalking them
OL,10,Fattended the property, a court has
OL,11,Fheard.
OL,13,FLeicester Crown Court heard that Karen
OL,14,FSpragg, 61, and 24-year-old Julia
OL,15,FWandelt, who claims to be the missing
OL,16,Fgirl, visited the McCanns' home in
OL,17,FLeicestershire on December 7 last year.
OL,19,FThe next day, a letter was posted
OL,20,Fthrough the door.
